template file which vim automatically loads when I open vim in certain directory
-------------------------------
Aperculum: how do I make a template file which vim automatically loads when I open vim in certain directory
[09:33] Heptite: Aperculum: :autocmd BufRead,BufNewFile /path/to/directory/* source /path/to/template
[09:34] Heptite: Erm, not source, read
[09:34] Heptite: Aperculum: :autocmd BufRead,BufNewFile /path/to/directory/* read /path/to/template
[09:34] Aperculum: I'll put that in my .vimrc

